c0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t m1dda x61 h34 y8c2 ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Seniors: Study Questions 13 and 14, and note. Search for the verses in this </div><div class="t ma57 x28 h34 y6d3 ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">epistle in which &quot;grace,&quot; &quot;peace,&quot; &quot;faith,&quot; apd &quot;love&quot; occur. </div><div class="t m1575 x61 h34 y4ed ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Children: Review the story of &quot;Abraham and Isaac.&quot; </div><div class="t m842 x4a h34 yc3 ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">7. </div><div class="t m121d x64 h34 y122a ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Seniors: Review the lesson. Study topics under &quot;Personal Applications.&quot; </div><div class="t m1a5 x61 h34 y478 ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Children: Revjew test questions, memory verses, and Memory Gems. </div><div class="t m21e9 x77 h34 y936 ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">THE LESSON </div><div class="t m48b x36 h1 ycf1 ff1 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m40b x66 h1 y609 ff1 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How does the apostle begin his final injunction? Eph. 6:10. </div><div class="t m1c9 x29 he yafa ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">NomE.—Not by human wisdom, not by knowledge, skill, art, or hu-</div><div class="t me4e x4a he y810 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">man combinations, not by any of these singly or altogether, do men </div><div class="t m390 x4a he y40f ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">stand for God and eternal life, but only by the power and might of God. </div><div class="t mae7 x36 h1 y54f ff1 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m706 x66 h1 yf53 ff1 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">With what must the soldier of Christ be protected? Verse 11. </div><div class="t meec x29 h1 y3c4 ff1 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">NOTE.—&quot;The </div><div class="t m139 x51 he y79f ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">armor,&quot; literally the panoply,—a complete suit of </div><div class="t m341 x4a he y86d ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">defensive armor,—supplied by God. During Paul&apos;s two years of im-</div><div class="t m8d x4a he y122c ff4 fs0 fc0 sc